6
00:00:22,200 --> 00:00:23,830
Ragnarok.

7
00:00:23,830 --> 00:00:31,109
Battles, earthquakes, fire, blood, a giant wolf, groaning dwarves, and Loki, who is the worst.

8
00:00:31,540 --> 00:00:33,540
