9
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:35,610
Because he dies. Oh! Spoiler alert!

10
00:00:45,470 --> 00:00:47,499
In many versions of the norse myths

11
00:00:47,500 --> 00:00:51,220
Ragnarok is the conclusion of one Loki story that we've already covered.

12
00:00:51,290 --> 00:00:55,959
You might remember a few weeks ago when we talked about the beloved god Baldr and his brother Hodr,

13
00:00:56,230 --> 00:01:01,059
How Loki tricked Hodr into killing Baldr by throwing a dart made of mistletoe and then

14
