While Loki may have succeeded in getting rid of Baldr his pleasure is short-lived.

17
00:01:14,800 --> 00:01:21,040
When the rest of the Aesir, the Norse gods of the sky, figure out they've been duped they fly into various rages,

18
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:24,300
Loki gets scared and poof! Amscrays outta Asgard's way.

19
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:28,600
The rest of the Aesir form a posse to bring Loki to justice.

20
00:01:28,970 --> 00:01:32,000
Loki decides to hide out in a cave near Frananger Falls.

21
